Jordan has boosted its bids for U.S.soft and hard wheat under Export Bonus, private export sourcessaid.    Jordan today bid 74 dlrs per tonne for soft wheat and 75dlrs per tonne for hard red winter wheat in its tender for225,000 tonnes of hard and soft wheat for April throughNovember shipment. Earlier today, USDA rejected its bids of 70dlrs for both varieties, they said. Reuter&#3;